# dir "users"
directory "users" contains files located in: /var/lib/AccountsService/users/
  # rafael
  # guest
  # root

# wallpaper
the image "piedras-rojas.jpg" used as the greeter wallpaper should be put in: /usr/share/lightdm-webkit/themes/lightdm-webkit-theme-aether/src/img/wallpapers/

Enable touchpad tapping:
copy the =40-libinput.conf= file into =/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/40-libinput.conf=